- Flows_old
Flows of the old systems calculated by Anders. Contains five folders depending on how radii are calculated, 4, 5, 6, 7 for the sampling time 10^X fs, and mean for the Method 2.

- max_flow.ipynb
Notebook containing the code to calculate the conductivity, and some of the plots vs max-Flows

- calc_max_flow_example.py
Example code for how to calculate the max-flow for both the old and new system, set up to run as "python calc_max_flow_example.py --index X" where X is the index of the system you want to calculate the max-flow for. Can be parallelized in a slurm job array as seen in run.sh.

- run.sh
Run script for calc_max_flow_example.py

- enviroment_maxflow.yml
Conda environment for calc_max_flow_example.py. Can be installed with "conda env create -f environment_maxflow.yml" 

- Max_flow.pptx
Presentation of the results from 15/12/2025

- electrolytes_flow.pkl.gz
Pickle file containing the flow for the new electrolytes, is used in max_flow.ipynb